OL,3,CImprovements to district hospital
OL,4,Cdelayed by at least a decade
OL,6,FThe Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,7,Fconfirmed on Monday, 20 Jan, that the
OL,8,Fnew emergency care centre at
OL,9,FPlymouth's Derriford Hospital will be
OL,10,Fprioritised, along with the women and
OL,11,Fchildren's hospital in Truro.
OL,13,FConstruction on both is expected to
OL,14,Fbegin before 2030, but several other
OL,15,Fhospital improvement programmes, like
OL,16,FNorth Devon District and Torbay
OL,17,FHospitals, have been pushed back.
OL,19,FWhich hospitals are part of the
OL,20,Fprogramme?
