OL,3,CImprovements to district hospital
OL,4,Cdelayed by at least a decade
OL,6,FAfter coming to power last year,
OL,7,FLabour's Chancellor Rachel Reeves said
OL,8,F"tough choices" would need to be made
OL,9,Fin a bid to deal with the
OL,10,F"catastrophic" state of the public
OL,11,Ffinances.
OL,13,FThe hospitals scheme was paused after
OL,14,Fit was deemed by Wes Streeting as
OL,15,F"undeliverable and unaffordable".
OL,17,FA review was then carried out while
OL,18,FNHS bosses warned that patient safety
OL,19,Fwas at risk.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
