OL,6,FNow the government has set out a
OL,7,Ftimeline for when work on each of the
OL,8,FWest Country's schemes will commence:
OL,10,FThe Department for Health and Social
OL,11,FCare has classified the hospitals into
OL,12,Fthree categories, with the first two
OL,13,Ffalling into 'Wave One' of the newly
OL,14,Frevised programme.
OL,16,FWes Streeting told MPs on Monday:
OL,17,F"Projects in wave zero are already in
OL,18,Fthe advanced stages of development and
OL,19,Fwill be completed within the next
OL,20,Fthree years.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
