OL,4,Cdelayed by at least a decade
OL,6,F"Wave one schemes will begin
OL,7,Fconstruction between 2025 and 2030",
OL,8,Fhe added.
OL,10,F"Wave three includes nine schemes
OL,11,Fwhich will start construction between
OL,12,F2035 and 2039.
OL,14,FThis means construction for the
OL,15,Fupgrade to North Devon District
OL,16,FHospital may not begin for up to 14
OL,17,Fyears, while work to rebuild Torbay
OL,18,Fhas been put off for at least seven.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
