OL,4,Cdelayed by at least a decade
OL,6,FLabour MP Jayne Kirkham, who
OL,7,Frepresents Truro and Falmouth, said
OL,8,Fit's right that the government has
OL,9,Fprioritised both Derriford and the new
OL,10,Fwomen and children's hospital in Truro.
OL,12,F"I'm really really pleased that it's
OL,13,Fin the first wave and will be
OL,14,Fcommenced before the end of the
OL,15,Fparliament. That enabling work has now
OL,16,Fbeen signed off, so we can get going
OL,17,Fon the ground work and finally deliver
OL,18,Fthis project.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
