OL,3,CImprovements to district hospital
OL,4,Cdelayed by at least a decade
OL,6,F"Wes Streeting, when we came into
OL,7,Fpower, was very honest, and said some
OL,8,Fof these projects would struggle. The
OL,9,Fmoney wasn't there. I'm so pleased it
OL,10,F(women and children's hospital) has
OL,11,Fbeen prioritised by this Labour
OL,12,Fgovernment now and it will be
OL,13,Fdelivered."
OL,15,FMs Kirkham said it's "really really
OL,16,Ffrustrating" that other hospital
OL,17,Fupgrades have been delayed, but
OL,18,Fclaimed the money simply wasn't there
OL,19,Ffor the programmes beyond March 2025.
