OL,6,FBen Maguire, the Liberal Democrat MP
OL,7,Ffor North Cornwall, said: "It's
OL,8,Fpositive to see the Women and
OL,9,FChildren's Hospital at Treliske, as
OL,10,Fwell as Derriford's Emergency Care
OL,11,FHospital, prioritised as 'Wave 1'.
OL,13,F"These projects are vital for the
OL,14,Fregion and must get moving swiftly.
OL,16,F"But for my North Cornwall
OL,17,Fconstituents who rely on North Devon
OL,18,F(District) Hospital - with facilities
OL,19,Fthat are quite literally crumbling...
OL,20,Fit is simply not good enough."
OL,26,@zD@ApmzD@Jpn
