OL,6,FHe added: "Patients need modern,
OL,7,Freliable healthcare NOW."
OL,9,FGideon Amos, Liberal Democrat MP for
OL,10,FTaunton and Wellington, said the
OL,11,Fimprovements to Musgrove Park Hospital
OL,12,Fhave come "far too late."
OL,14,FSam Higginson, CEO at Royal Devon
OL,15,FUniversity Healthcare NHS Foundation
OL,16,FTrust has also criticised the
OL,17,Fannouncement by the health secretary
OL,18,Fon Monday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
