OL,6,FMr Higginson said: "We are
OL,7,Fdisappointed for both our staff and
OL,8,Fthe communities of North Devon, that
OL,9,Fthe critical nature of North Devon
OL,10,FDistrict Hospital and the need for
OL,11,Furgent investment has not been fully
OL,12,Frecognised in today's announcement.
OL,26,@nD@TOU
